column5: I will be going to Tobin in early June and would appreciate ant info inn regards to where to go and what to use on the lake. Thanks, Bill

Hey Bill,I fish tobin a bunch every year, let me know your email address, and i will send you all the info you will ever need, like web pages, cabins, boat rental, hot spots, presentaion, etc.Hope to hear from you!Pikeman
Hey Pikeman, my email address is [email protected] thanks and looking forward to your info.
